OL,3,CNew battle over #250 million A38 Derby
OL,4,Cupgrade decision
OL,6,FA decision on whether a major #250
OL,7,Fmillion upgrade project can go ahead
OL,8,Fin Derby is to be made in the courts
OL,9,Ffor a second time in May.
OL,11,FNational Highways has confirmed in a
OL,12,Fstatement a new court date has been
OL,13,Fpencilled in for Tuesday, May 14,
OL,14,Fwhich will determine if the project on
OL,15,Fone of can go ahead.
