OL,3,CNew battle over #250 million A38 Derby
OL,4,Cupgrade decision
OL,6,FThe firm says it is "still committed"
OL,7,Fto delivering the "essential" #250m
OL,8,Froad scheme, which involves expanding
OL,9,Fthe road from four to six lanes around
OL,10,Fthe three junctions at Little Eaton,
OL,11,FMarkeaton and Kingsway and
OL,12,Fconstructing flyovers and underpasses.
OL,14,FBut campaigners say the project should
OL,15,Fnot go ahead.
OL,17,FIn August last year Transport Minister
OL,18,FMark Harper gave the A38 scheme the go-
OL,19,Fahead.
