OL,3,CNew battle over #250 million A38 Derby
OL,4,Cupgrade decision
OL,6,FBut in December at the Royal Courts of
OL,7,FJustice, Mrs Justice Jefford granted
OL,8,Fthe case permission to go to trial
OL,9,Fafter hearing arguments from both
OL,10,FRichard Buxton Solicitors,
OL,11,Frepresenting the Stop the A38
OL,12,FExpansion campaign group, as well as
OL,13,Ffrom the Department for Transport and
OL,14,FNational Highways.
OL,16,FThe Stop the A38 Expansion group
OL,17,Fbelieve the project is a waste of
OL,18,Fpublic money.
