OL,3,CNew battle over #250 million A38 Derby
OL,4,Cupgrade decision
OL,6,FCampaigners say the multimillion-pound
OL,7,Fworks will increase carbon emissions,
OL,8,Fincrease traffic and destroy thousands
OL,9,Fof trees including centuries-old ones
OL,10,Fat Markeaton Park.
OL,12,FThey say the A38 expansion is "not the
OL,13,Fright solution" to alleviate
OL,14,Fcongestion on one of Derby's main
OL,15,Froutes.
OL,17,FNational Highways says the legal
OL,18,Fdebate surrounding the A38 project is
OL,19,Fbased on an "economic assessment" and
OL,20,F"alleged failures in the application
OL,21,Fprocess".
