OL,4,Cupgrade decision
OL,6,FOn the Stop the A38 Crowd Funding
OL,7,Fpage, campaigners say: "One of our
OL,8,Flegal challenge grounds is that the
OL,9,FA38 was approved with an over four-
OL,10,Fyear-old and secretive economic
OL,11,Fassessment that didn't include recent
OL,12,Fchanges in treasury guidance or the
OL,13,Fimpacts of inflation or carbon pricing
OL,14,Fon the benefit-cost ratio (BCR) of the
OL,15,Fscheme.
OL,17,F"We've always said the A38 expansion
OL,18,Fis a waste of public money, especially
OL,19,Fduring the cost of living crisis and
OL,20,Fclimate crisis.
