OL,6,F"The #250 million should be invested
OL,7,Fin public transport and active travel
OL,8,Fto help tackle these crises.
OL,10,F"Instead, the Government is
OL,11,Fprioritising the interests of private
OL,12,Fcompanies who plan to profit from the
OL,13,Fincreased road capacity by building
OL,14,Feven more car-dependent developments
OL,15,Fon greenfield sites near the A38.
OL,17,F"This is public money being used to
OL,18,Fline the pockets of private
OL,19,Fbusinesses."
