OL,3,CNew battle over #250 million A38 Derby
OL,4,Cupgrade decision
OL,6,FThis is not the first time the A38
OL,7,Fproject has been discussed at length
OL,8,Fat the High Court.
OL,10,FIn 2021 the scheme was granted
OL,11,Fapproval by the Government before the
OL,12,Fconsent order was officially quashed
OL,13,Fby the High Court in 2021 following a
OL,14,Fsuccessful legal challenge regarding
OL,15,Fclimate concerns.
OL,17,FNational Highways said it would know
OL,18,Fthe final decision between six to
OL,19,Feight weeks after the court date in
OL,20,FMay.
