OL,6,FA statement from National Highways on
OL,7,Fits website says: "The next hearing on
OL,8,Fground one (economic assessment) is
OL,9,Fexpected on Tuesday, May 14, 2024.
OL,11,F"We should be informed of the outcome
OL,12,Fof this hearing six to eight weeks
OL,13,Fafterwards.
OL,15,F"Due to the outstanding legal
OL,16,Fchallenge, we've been unable to fully
OL,17,Fremobilise the project team or
OL,18,Fcommence the process of appointing a
OL,19,Fnew contractor for this scheme.
