OL,6,F"We understand this may be
OL,7,Fdisappointing for you to hear as it
OL,8,Fwill inevitably delay our programme
OL,9,Ffor the project further.
OL,11,F"We're still committed to delivering
OL,12,Fthese essential upgrades to the three
OL,13,Fjunctions along the A38 through Derby.
OL,14,FWe'll continue to update you as we
OL,15,Fknow more."
